"title": "6705: peace, believers' experience of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6705: peace, believers' experience of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Peace is the birthright of every believer in all circumstances. It is found only in God and is maintained through having a close relationship with him.</p>\n<h2>Peace for believers in differing situations</h2>\n<h3>In times of sickness, pressure and hardships</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:1-Ps41:3\">PSA 41:1–41:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:28\">MAT 11:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:13-Job1:22\">JOB 1:13–1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:7-Job2:10\">JOB 2:7–2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:22-Acts16:25\">ACT 16:22–16:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:7-2Cor12:10\">2CO 12:7–12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:16-2Tim4:18\">2TI 4:16–4:18</a></p>\n<h3>In times of death and grief</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1-John14:3\">JHN 14:1–14:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:25-Job19:26\">JOB 19:25–19:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:18-2Kgs22:20\">2KI 22:18–22:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:1-Isa57:2\">ISA 57:1–57:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:13-1Thess4:18\">1TH 4:13–4:18</a></p>\n<h2>The effects of peace for believers</h2>\n<h3>Forgiveness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:60\">ACT 7:60</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:17-Rom12:19\">ROM 12:17–12:19</a></p>\n<h3>Encouragement</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:3-2Cor1:6\">2CO 1:3–1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:11-Phil4:13\">PHP 4:11–4:13</a></p>\n<h3>Health and healing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:30\">PRO 14:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:18-Isa57:19\">ISA 57:18–57:19</a></p>\n<h3>Security</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:33\">PRO 1:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:21-Acts27:26\">ACT 27:21–27:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28\">ROM 8:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:35-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:35–8:39</a></p>\n<h3>Hope</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">ROM 15:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1-Rom5:5\">ROM 5:1–5:5</a></p>\n<h2>How believers maintain peace</h2>\n<h3>Through remaining in Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:4-John15:7\">JHN 15:4–15:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:33\">JHN 16:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:1-Rom5:5\">ROM 5:1–5:5</a></p>\n<h3>Through living by the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:6\">ROM 8:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:17-Rom14:19\">ROM 14:17–14:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22\">GAL 5:22</a></p>\n<h3>Through obedience to God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:8-Josh1:9\">JOS 1:8–1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:165-Ps119:167\">PSA 119:165–119:167</a></p>\n<h3>Through prayer and meditation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:6-Phil4:9\">PHP 4:6–4:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:1-Ps1:3\">PSA 1:1–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:3\">ISA 26:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:1-1Tim2:2\">1TI 2:1–2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Final peace in death for believers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:2\">ISA 57:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:13\">REV 14:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:19-2Kgs22:20\">2KI 22:19–22:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:29\">LUK 2:29</a></p>\n<h2>Hope of future peace for believers</h2>\n<h3>Peace in heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:4\">1PE 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:1-John14:3\">JHN 14:1–14:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:13-1Thess4:14\">1TH 4:13–4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:9-Rev7:17\">REV 7:9–7:17</a></p>\n<h3>Peace in God's new creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1-Rev21:4\">REV 21:1–21:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:6-Isa11:9\">ISA 11:6–11:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:18-Rom8:23\">ROM 8:18–8:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:3-Rev22:5\">REV 22:3–22:5</a></p>",
